Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing Evening’ game
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday evening’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “All or Nothing Evening” game were:
01-02-04-10-11-13-14-15-19-20-23-24
(one, two, four, ten, eleven, thirteen, fourteen, fifteen, nineteen, twenty, twenty-three, twenty-four)
